00:07:02.700 --> 00:07:09.960
ظآزI want to turn back
and walk with youظآز

00:07:10.539 --> 00:07:12.419
You drank all my beer.

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:20.232
ظآزYour freedomظآز

00:07:21.099 --> 00:07:22.218
We had the beer

