00:07:32.687 --> 00:07:38.680
ظآزA cup of wine full of sorrowظآز

00:07:38.887 --> 00:07:45.119
ظآزLooking up,
there's the beautiful starry skyظآز

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:48.640
ظآزYou told meظآز

00:07:48.675 --> 00:07:53.298
ظآزIt would shine like the starsظآز

00:07:53.299 --> 00:07:54.419
You're drunk.

00:07:55.419 --> 00:07:56.380
